These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-1::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, august, june, january
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, coffee, cola, almond-milk
House: futuristic, colonial, wooden, craftsman
1. the wooden house is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
2. the craftsman house is the person drinking mirinda##1
3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far left##1
4. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking coffee is between the wooden house and the person who's birthday is in august##2
6. the colonial house is the person drinking cola##1
7. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Birthday        | june | january  | august | march  |
| Beverage         | almond-milk    | coffee  | mirinda       | cola     |
| House   | wooden     | futuristic | craftsman       | colonial |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  firefighter, electrician, accountant, architect
House: palace, modern, tower, ranch-style
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, poppy, dahlia, amaryllis
1. the electrician is on the far left##1
2. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the firefighter##1
3. the person who growspoppy is on the far left##1
4. the person who growsamaryllis is between the ranch-style house and the architect##2
5. the ranch-style house is the person who growspoppy##1
6. the palace house is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
7. the tower house is the person who growsdahlia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |      4       |
| Job         | electrician | firefighter    | architect  | accountant |
| House   | ranch-style  | palace  | modern   | tower    |
| Flower         | poppy | amaryllis | balloon-flower | dahlia      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-3::.
City: colone, miami, nizza, prague
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, ship, trike, bike
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, pear, watermelon, mango
1. the person eating pear is between the person eating mango and the person traveling to miami##2
2. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person eating blueberry##1
3. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
4. the person traveling to nizza is on the far right##1
5. the person driving the ship is on the far left##1
6. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
7. the person eating watermelon is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| City      | miami | prague         | colone   | nizza    |
| Transport         | ship | bike | quad-bike | trike |
| Food   | watermelon   | pear        | mango      | blueberry   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-4::.
4 different pets are kept: goat, turtle, mouse, dog
There 4 different types of food: potato, pineapple, watermelon, corn
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, documentary, time-travel, action
1. the person watching time-travel movies is on the far left##1
2. the person watching animation movies is between the person watching action movies and the owner of the dog##2
3. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1
4. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person eating watermelon##1
5. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
6. the person watching action movies is between the person eating potato and the person watching documentary movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |   4    |
| Pet   | dog        | turtle   | goat | mouse |
| Food         | watermelon | potato | pineapple    | corn |
| Movie-Genre     | time-travel       | animation     | action       | documentary    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-5::.
City: nizza, paris, miami, marseilles
House: cottage, tower, townhouse, gothic-revival
There are 4 different nationalities: french, spanish, turkish, canadian
1. the canadian is between the person traveling to nizza and the person traveling to paris##2
2. the canadian is the person traveling to marseilles##1
3. the townhouse house is on the far right##1
4. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1
5. the french is on the right of the turkish##1
6. the turkish is on the right of the tower house##1
7. the canadian is between the turkish and the cottage house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |      3      |     4      |
| City   | nizza | marseilles      | paris       | miami   |
| House      | cottage   | tower  | gothic-revival | townhouse     |
| Nationality      | spanish     | canadian | turkish        | french |

