.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, japanese, australian, german
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, satire, crime, epic
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: lily, daisy, daffodil, tulip
1. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
2. the dutch is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
3. the dutch is on the right of the person who growslily##1
4. the person who growstulip is on the left of the japanese##1
5. the person watching adventure movies is between the person watching epic movies and the person who growsdaffodil##2
6. the japanese is between the dutch and the australian##2
7. the person who growslily is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Nationality    | australian | japanese  | dutch | german      |
| Movie-Genre   | crime  | epic  | adventure | satire |
| Flower   | tulip | lily | daisy | daffodil     |

