.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-7::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, ritmeester, cain, blend
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, photography, video-games, magic-tricks
City: miami, new-york, venice, berlin
1. the person traveling to berlin is the person who's hobby is photography##1
2. the person traveling to venice is the person who's hobby is singing##1
3. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far left##1
4. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
5. the cain-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1
6. the ritmeester-smoker is between the person who's hobby is photography and the person who's hobby is video-games##2
7. the blend-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Cigar          | cain  | ritmeester    | blend | bolivar  |
| Hobby   | video-games | magic-tricks       | photography        | singing    |
| City         | new-york | miami | berlin  | venice |

