.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-8::.
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, australian, colombian, mexican
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, february, august, may
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, cycling, swimming, parkour
1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
2. the person who's birthday is in february is between the person who's sport is parkour and the australian##2
3. the colombian is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
4. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
5. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the mexican##1
6. the colombian is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |      4      |
| Nationality         | mexican  | australian | colombian | argentine |
| Birthday   | june  | may | february   | august         |
| Sport           | soccer | swimming  | cycling   | parkour      |

