.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-9::.
City: san-francisco, hannover, miami, boston
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, december, november, august
House: colonial, palace, gothic-revival, victorian
1. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the victorian house##1
2. the person who's birthday is in december is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
3. the palace house is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
4. the person who's birthday is in november is the person traveling to hannover##1
5. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
6. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far right##1
7. the person who's birthday is in december is between the gothic-revival house and the person who's birthday is in march##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| City          | boston  | san-francisco    | miami | hannover       |
| Birthday         | august | december | march  | november |
| House   | gothic-revival   | victorian      | palace  | colonial     |

