.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-10::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, prince, game, oliveros
4 different pets are kept: fish, snake, chinchilla, lizard
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, golf, rugby, baseball
1. the owner of the lizard is on the far left##1
2. the game-smoker is on the far left##1
3. the prince-smoker is between the old-henry-smoker and the owner of the snake##2
4. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far right##1
6. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1
7. the person who's sport is baseball is the owner of the lizard##1
8. the person who's sport is sailing is the oliveros-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Cigar          | game      | oliveros | prince | old-henry |
| Pet         | lizard   | snake  | fish | chinchilla |
| Sport   | baseball | sailing   | golf | rugby |

