.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-11::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, dannemann, bluemaster, alhambra
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, sprite, soy-milk, hot-chocolate
4 different games are played: scrabble, monopoly, whist, poker
1. the dannemann-smoker is on the right of the game-smoker##1
2. the person playing whist is the dannemann-smoker##1
3. the person playing scrabble is between the person drinking sprite and the person drinking soy-milk##2
4. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person playing scrabble and the alhambra-smoker##2
5. the person drinking soy-milk is the person playing poker##1
6. the person drinking milk is the person playing monopoly##1
7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person playing scrabble##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| Cigar    | alhambra  | bluemaster | game | dannemann     |
| Beverage   | milk | soy-milk   | hot-chocolate  | sprite    |
| Game     | monopoly        | poker       | scrabble      | whist |

