1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
2. the person watching western movies is between the person who's birthday is in july and the person traveling to miami##2
3. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
4. the person who's birthday is in june is the person watching romance movies##1
5. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
6. the person who's birthday is in may is the person traveling to berlin##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |     3      |    4    |
| Birthday   | june | may  | july       | september   |
| City      | miami     | berlin | san-francisco | prague |
| Movie-Genre        | romance        | western | zombie     | mystery |

