.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-14::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, pall-mall, swisher, vegafina
4 different games are played: scrabble, monopoly, snooker, whist
4 different pets are kept: bird, hamster, fish, guinea-pig
1. the person playing scrabble is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
2. the owner of the fish is the swisher-smoker##1
3. the owner of the fish is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1
4. the person playing whist is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
5. the owner of the hamster is between the person playing snooker and the swisher-smoker##2
6. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far right##1
7. the owner of the hamster is the vegafina-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Cigar           | pall-mall | vegafina | swisher    | aristoff   |
| Game   | snooker      | monopoly   | whist | scrabble |
| Pet     | bird     | hamster       | fish        | guinea-pig    |

