4. the person eating artichoke is between the person who's birthday is in november and the cape-cod house##2
5. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1
6. the colonial house is between the victorian house and the person who's birthday is in october##2
7. the person who's birthday is in august is the cape-cod house##1

