.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-17::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, fantasy, crime, comedy
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: dahlia, iris, zinnia, poppy
There are 4 different favourite colors: turquise, black, ivory, light-blue
1. the person watching family movies is on the far left##1
2. the person who growszinnia is between the person watching comedy movies and the person who likes ivory##2
3. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the person who likes black##1
4. the person who likes turquise is on the far right##1
5. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
6. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
7. the person watching crime movies is the person who likes turquise##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | family    | fantasy | comedy           | crime |
| Flower       | dahlia | zinnia    | iris          | poppy   |
| Color      | ivory  | black   | light-blue | turquise  |

