.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-18::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: apricot, black, ebony, brown
4 different games are played: scrabble, go, poker, domino
There 4 different types of food: peach, pear, potato, grapefruit
1. the person playing poker is the person who likes black##1
2. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the person eating peach##1
3. the person playing domino is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1
4. the person who likes apricot is between the person playing poker and the person playing scrabble##2
5. the person eating pear is on the left of the person who likes brown##1
6. the person eating grapefruit is between the person who likes black and the person eating peach##2
7. the person playing domino is the person eating grapefruit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Color      | ebony | apricot | black     | brown   |
| Game   | scrabble | domino        | poker  | go  |
| Food           | peach      | grapefruit         | pear | potato |

