.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-19::.
City: rome, paris, edinburgh, marseilles
There 4 different types of food: pomegranate, lettuce, orange, cherry
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, writing, rock-climbing, hiking
1. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
2. the person eating cherry is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
3. the person traveling to rome is on the far left##1
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person traveling to marseilles##1
5. the person eating pomegranate is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
6. the person who's hobby is hiking is between the person eating lettuce and the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| City         | rome        | marseilles  | edinburgh | paris   |
| Food       | cherry | pomegranate | orange    | lettuce |
| Hobby   | dancing        | rock-climbing     | hiking       | writing      |

