.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  scientist, analyst, teacher, architect
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, begonia, daisy, iris
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, aristoff, siglo, montecristo
1. the person who growstulip is on the far left##1
2. the scientist is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1
3. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
4. the teacher is on the far right##1
5. the montecristo-smoker is the person who growsiris##1
6. the person who growsbegonia is between the architect and the siglo-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Job        | architect | analyst | scientist | teacher |
| Flower         | tulip       | begonia     | daisy   | iris   |
| Cigar   | davidoff | aristoff | siglo | montecristo |

 